<P>The race originally called Ortain were a small grey skinned reptilian =
race.=20
The Ortain created machines in their own image specifically to do jobs =
and work=20
such as war that an Ortain could not do as efficiently. </P>
<P>The machines were created with complex AI and eventually were =
regarded as=20
people along side the Ortain race. The Ortain machines shared most of =
the same=20
laws and had positions of power where they were suited. </P>
<P>Some event not described by history saw the Ortain wiped out as a =
species=20
however the AI created by the Ortain lived on and filled the gaps in the =
jobs=20
and power structure left by the cataclysmic event. </P>
<P>The machines considered and treated themselves as people amongst =
their race=20
as the original Ortain had done, and although largely designed for war =
attempted=20
to carry on in jobs they ill fitted.</P>
<P>The Ortain were built for war and do not have feelings regarding =
comfort or=20
personal space, this has allowed them to develop the Compact Troop =
Compartment,=20
a smaller way to carry large amounts of infantry on their ships.</P>
<P>The machine Ortain are an extremely paranoid race and can be very =
insular in=20
behaviour. They are very badly equipped for diplomacy and fitting in =
with other=20
species. They are however well equipped for war. Many still consider it =
their=20
job to subdue other races because of in built behaviours originally =
designed to=20
protect the Ortain.</P>
<P>The preferred weapon of the Ortain is the Rail Gun with Ion =
technology and=20
they focus on Power and Shields with Energy=20
Research.</P></FONT></DIV></BODY></HTML>

